(gen_random_uuid(),'boda-boda-fleet-ng','Motorcycle Taxi Fleet','transportation','NG','Nigeria','small','medium','Purchase 2-5 motorcycles and hire riders on daily rental or commission basis. Operator collects fixed daily fee and handles maintenance and licensing.','Motorcycles are dominant last-mile transport across Africa. Rising fuel costs and congestion make bikes faster and cheaper for short trips.','Daily rider fee or 60/40 commission split. Additional revenue from bike branding.','{"Rider accidents","Motorcycle theft","Regulatory bans","Fuel volatility","Rider turnover"}','2-3 bikes > 10-20 bikes > add electric > fleet management platform',800000,2500000,'NGN',120000,350000,54000,192500,4,10,'{"Business registration required","Tax ID (TIN) mandatory"}','{"Lagos","Abuja","Port Harcourt","Ibadan","Kano"}','[{"item":"Equipment & Setup","cost":"₦280,000"},{"item":"Inventory","cost":"₦200,000"},{"item":"Rent (3mo)","cost":"₦120,000"},{"item":"Staff (3mo)","cost":"₦80,000"},{"item":"Marketing","cost":"₦80,000"},{"item":"Working Capital","cost":"₦40,000"}]'::jsonb,'{"transport","motorbike","okada","boda","ng","west"}','seed',0,0,0,NOW(),NOW()),
